Tools of War (The Vietnam Experience)
Boston Publishing Company | 1984 | ISBN 0939526131 | English | 184 pages | PDF | 23.3 MB

The Vietnam Experience was published as a 25-volume illustrated history of the Vietnam War. The first volume, Setting the Stage, was published in 1981, and the final volume, War in the Shadows, was published in 1988. Brought to you in wonderful detail through vivid photography and engaging, informative text
